I had this really expensive blow, I only got a .5 because a g was ¬£92 and wasn't a fan at all it made me really stuffy and kinda hard to breathe because it was just clogging me up.

I hot plated the rest of it a couple days later and it was the best blow I've done, awesome gear and so think the hot plate making it more powder like made it so it actually got absorbed better too and more high and way less stuffy.

It comes down to each production team, I believe q dance presses to very accurate with their dosages however I had some of their visa pills before and I think they were only meant to be 220mg but a quarter would be enough to have a good roll, even half would have me a bit floored and a full pill being just way too much.

But I promise you these massive producers aren't going to be sad if they lose some weight by accidental over dosing their pills with the volume they shift.

It's probably more common for pills to be underdosed but trust me some pills these days are just too strong, with crystals it's effortless to weigh out the dose you want and put it in a capsule or rizzla  or water or anything, I think some people would be pleasently surprised with how great a 120mg roll would feel compared to 200mg+

2cb pills are very common to be underdosed, especially yellow Batman's I think they're quite often around 10mg, I've been hooked up with some Dutch ones before which were deffo 22mg which were just little pink squares with '2cb' imprinted on them they were dope.

They could have been weak and that's why they didn't hit you much but I do honestly recommend giving 2cb another go it is a very nice drug ngl.

Lsd usually comes in discreet envelope and is the easiest option stealth wise and only order under their real name, a PO box is a good option but I've never bothered.

A trusted seller will usually provide good stealth and even decoys and as long as they don't have parents which swoop through their mail they're good to go.

With that being said be careful and don't go overboard and you should be good unless you order stupid amounts the risk is quite low and only order domestically don't order from another country as the risk is significantly increased, some people still go for it though the risk varies country to country with Netherlands usually being the most bait to order from.
